com.cloudera.oryx.als.common.rescorer

Class MultiRescorerProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cloudera.oryx.als.common.rescorer.AbstractRescorerProvider
      • com.cloudera.oryx.als.common.rescorer.MultiRescorerProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RescorerProvider

    public final class MultiRescorerProvider
extends AbstractRescorerProvider
    Convenience implementation that will aggregate the behavior of multiple RescorerProviders. It will filter an item if any of the given instances filter it, and will rescore by applying the rescorings in the given order.
    Author:
    Sean Owen
    See Also:
    MultiRescorer, MultiLongPairRescorer
